{"tha-ap376:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap376:0.2":"Bodhivandanavagga ","tha-ap376:0.3":"4 Pattipupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap376:1.1":"“Yada nibbayi sambuddho, ","tha-ap376:1.2":"mahesi padumuttaro; ","tha-ap376:1.3":"Samagamma jana sabbe, ","tha-ap376:1.4":"sariram niharanti te. ","tha-ap376:2.1":"Niharante sariramhi, ","tha-ap376:2.2":"vajjamanasu bherisu; ","tha-ap376:2.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap376:2.4":"pattipuppham apujayim. ","tha-ap376:3.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap376:3.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap376:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap376:3.4":"sarirapujite phalam. ","tha-ap376:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap376:4.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap376:4.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap376:4.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap376:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap376:5.2":"Mama buddhassa santike; ","tha-ap376:5.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap376:5.4":"Katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap376:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap376:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap376:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap376:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pattipupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap376:8.1":"Pattipupphiyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}